 Higher\nresolution data are needed in order to test the scaling relations between\noutflow velocity and both star-formation rate and star-formation rate surface\ndensity predicted by theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 May 2012 20:00:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 Sep 2012 20:37:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
