e for the fast rise and slow decline. We define a class of SN\n2001ay-like SNe Ia, which will show an anti-Phillips relation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 May 2012 20:04:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
