t steady state observables. In our study we\nhave assumed small to medium size arrays (from 3 up to 16 sites) and values of\nthe ratio of coupling to dissipation rate $g/\\gamma \\sim 20$ which makes our\nresults implementable with current designs in Circuit QED and with near future\nphotonic crystal set ups.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 May 2012 15:57:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-01-15"}
